---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — bettervibe" noindex={true} showCta={false}>
    <main class="content">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 2, 2026</p>

        <h2>1. Controller</h2>
        <p>
            Dominik Grusemann<br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:dominik.grusemann@gmail.com"
                >dominik.grusemann@gmail.com</a
            >
        </p>

        <h2>2. What this site does</h2>
        <p>
            bettervibe.org is a static website that provides information about
            the bettervibe workshop. The site does not use cookies, does not
            use analytics or tracking tools, and does not collect personal
            data through forms or user accounts.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Hosting</h2>
        <p>
            This website is hosted on <strong>GitHub Pages</strong>, a service
            provided by GitHub, Inc. (a subsidiary of Microsoft Corporation),
            88 Colin P Kelly Jr St, San Francisco, CA 94107, USA.
        </p>
        <p>
            When you visit this site, GitHub may process your IP address,
            browser type, operating system, referrer URL, and timestamp as
            part of server log files. This processing is necessary to deliver
            the website and is based on our legitimate interest (Art. 6(1)(f)
            GDPR). GitHub's privacy statement is available at <a
                href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement"
                >docs.github.com</a
            >.
        </p>
        <p>
            GitHub, Inc. is certified under the EU-US Data Privacy Framework,
            which provides an adequate level of data protection for transfers
            of personal data from the EU to the US.
        </p>

        <h2>4. External links</h2>
        <p>
            This site links to third-party services (Luma for event
            registration, LinkedIn for instructor profiles). When you follow
            these links, you leave bettervibe.org and are subject to those
            services' own privacy policies. We have no control over their data
            processing.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Your rights</h2>
        <p>Under the GDPR, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Request access to your personal data (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Request rectification of inaccurate data (Art. 16 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Request erasure of your data (Art. 17 GDPR)</li>
            <li>Request restriction of processing (Art. 18 GDPR)</li>
            <li>
                Object to processing based on legitimate interest (Art. 21
                GDPR)
            </li>
            <li>
                Lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority (Art. 77 GDPR)
                — for Bavaria: Bayerisches Landesamt für Datenschutzaufsicht
                (BayLDA), Promenade 18, 91522 Ansbach
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            To exercise any of these rights, contact <a
                href="mailto:dominik.grusemann@gmail.com"
                >dominik.grusemann@gmail.com</a
            >.
        </p>
    </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .content {
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 120px 48px 80px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        line-height: 1.8;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: clamp(24px, 3vw, 32px);
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        letter-spacing: -1px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .last-updated {
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        margin-top: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .content :global(p),
    .content :global(li) {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-weight: 300;
        line-height: 1.9;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .content :global(ul) {
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .content :global(li) {
        margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .content :global(a) {
        color: var(--amber);
    }
    .content :global(a:hover) {
        color: #e8956f;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .content {
            padding: 100px 24px 60px;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .content {
            padding: 80px 16px 48px;
        }
    }
</style>
